OPS-VSI is OpenSwitch component test framework.
Developers does not need to install in on the Host python.

To install this package in the OpenSwitch source code build directory:
$> cd <TOP Level of OpenSwitch source repo>
$> make devenv_ct_init

The above command will install the ops-vsi in the sysroot of the current source build directory.
The installed files can be located at <ops-build dir>/build/tmp/sysroots/x86_64-linux/usr/lib/python

To use these installed files, one has to use the python install the above sysroot directory.
